%tr
  %td.wrapper
    %table{:border => "0", :cellpadding => "0", :cellspacing => "0"}
      %tr
        %td
          %p Hi there,
          %br
            = "Your volunteer application for #{@event.name} 2017 has been approved!"
          %br
          Please login to your account to accept or decline your position. The sooner you do, the more likely you will be to receive your shift preference!
          %br
          %br
          %table.btn.btn-primary{:border => "0", :cellpadding => "0", :cellspacing => "0"}
            %tbody
              %tr
                %td{:align => "left"}
                  %table{:border => "0", :cellpadding => "0", :cellspacing => "0"}
                    %tbody
                      %tr
                        %td
                          = link_to @url, target: "_blank" do
                            Login to accept / decline your spot
          %p We need to confirm all positions by September 23rd, so if you have not accepted your position by then, we'll assume you don't want it.
          %p Upon accepting your position, your saved credit card will be charged $15 for you Volunteer T-shirt.  If you accept your position and do not make your shift, you will be liable for the full cost of a ticket plus a penalty fee totalling $360.
          %p We'll be sending out more information within the next few weeks, so please watch your email.
          %br
          %p Much Love,
          %p Strawberry Fields